OL,8,Fclients through various means -
OL,9,Fdiverting most funds to the accounts
OL,10,Fof her friend Julie Atkins, who would
OL,11,Fthe pay some back to her.
OL,13,FThe thefts took place from estates
OL,14,Fhandled by Porter between 2006 and
OL,15,F2018. Restriction orders were then
OL,16,Fimposed on the finances of both women.
