OL,6,F"Laurna Porter breached her legal
OL,7,Fduties as a probate manager and abused
OL,8,Fher position of trust in taking funds
OL,9,Ffrom life-saving charities, as well as
OL,10,Ffrom families of the deceased.
OL,12,F"It must have been particularly
OL,13,Fdistressing for the families and
OL,14,Ffriends, who simply want to see their
OL,15,Floved one's last wishes properly
OL,16,Fexecuted.
OL,18,F"The CPS will now seek to recover any
OL,19,Favailable criminal proceeds from the
OL,20,Fdefendants, in order to compensate the
OL,21,Fbeneficiaries."
